###

@baseUrl = {{tunnel}}
@local = http://localhost:6969
@tunnel = https://strong-ads-roll.loca.lt/


### login

# @name login

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}


### Send Test

# @name create_test

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tests HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.access_token}}

{
  "config": {
    "0": true,
    "1": true
  },
  "device": "esp32",
  "test_type": "tremor"
}
